column_.text_:
Wow... Mind if I take a closer look at that fine piece of smithery
you've got there?
I gotta say, , you sure settle for nothing less than the best!
I gotta say, , you sure settle for nothing less than the best!

This thing has been honed to near perfection, but I've got a special
client that can take top-notch equipment to the next level.
If you're interested, just say the word!
I smell a new mission!
Ready for some action?
Let's kick some tail!
Work hard, play hard!
This'll be interesting.
Let's do our best!
Mission complete!
Easier than eatin' apples!
Baddies ain't got nothin' on you!
Great work today, team!
I knew we could do it!
Another satisfied client!
This won't do at all... There has to be a way...
Is something wrong?
Is something wrong?
Is something wrong?

Why, hello, lovely and generous skyfarers! Talk about perfect
timing!

I don't know if you've heard the news, but a meteorite crashed in
the eastern part of Zegagrande the other day.

Turns out it's not a cosmic rock at all but a big, mean, smashing
machine. The whole skydom's gone on high alert.

If I can't travel freely to sell my wares, I might as well hang up my
merchant hat right now.

A machine from beyond the Sky Realm, huh? You don't think it
could be an automagod, do you?

If it isn't, it definitely sounds like one. Obviously there's only one
way to be sure.

Ah, does it ring a bell? Well, the mission's available at the Quest
Counter, but fair warning—be prepared for a tough fight.
Sold! I'm up for the challenge!
Sold! I'm up for the challenge!
And that takes care of that.

Imagine fighting an army of those things. Ugh. Way to go,
team!

Hey, it looks like we can take on some new requests!
Gosh, they seem tough though. Want to check them out?

Hey, we can use that card to call up new crewmates! Let's find 
Siero and really get this party started!
I smell treasure!
Those sparkles mean one thing: treasure hunt!
Oh, sparkles! Do we have time for a quick detour?
Is that treasure? I wonder what it could be?

Look at that—you think there's treasure inside? Let's check
it out!
Up for a treasure challenge?

Oh, you're done exploring this area? That's fair—just don't
say I didn't warn ya!
Moving on? We can always come back later.
